1
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,200
Back then, the Eldest Princess supported me as a child emperor

2
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:51,840
and ruled behind the curtain.

3
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:54,900
The power in the court was almost entirely in her hands.

4
00:00:55,160 --> 00:00:58,000
Only by acting incompetent and unrestrained could I protect myself

5
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,160
and protect Ayan.

6
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,680
The price was

7
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:07,600
the fear of the world and a bad reputation.

8
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,530
I have been acting for so many years

9
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:11,120
that I'm used to it.

10
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:13,080
But I still don't understand

11
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,650
why you aren't afraid of me.

12
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,420
Why should I be afraid?

13
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:20,120
Being a tyrant keeps you safe

14
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:22,520
and lets you act crazy whenever you want.

15
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,120
How great is that?

16
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:27,600
For instance, when the head female official picked on me,

17
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:29,080
I beat her up right there.

18
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:31,400
And she couldn't reason with a crazy person.

19
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,400
How great is that?

20
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:35,120
Being crazy keeps you safe.

21
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,560
We...

22
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:54,360
Ayue.

23
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,960
In all your lives,

24
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,060
you must be safe and sound.

25
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,200
Even I

26
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,600
can't hurt you.

27
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:23,320
Aren't you with Ayue every day?

28
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:25,480
How do you not know what she likes?

29
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:37,240
Doesn't Sister Cangyue like your puppy?

30
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,000
Can you give her one?

31
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,240
No.

32
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:43,640
Puppies aren't toys. I can't give them away.

33
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,680
When will it get dark?

34
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,760
In about four hours.

35
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,840
Xiaoyue, let's go out and play.

36
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:41,960
Xiaoyue.

37
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,440
One times one is one.

38
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,360
One times two is two.

39
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,279
One times three is three.

40
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,240
Two times three is six.

41
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,240
Two times four is eight.

42
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,700
Three times three is nine.

43
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,120
Your Majesty.

44
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,200
What is it?

45
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,520
Your Majesty is truly handsome.

46
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,760
Jindou, Yuanbao!

47
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:20,680
Jindou, Yuanbao!

48
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,480
Yuanyuan!

49
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:26,360
Jindou and Yuanbao are missing.

50
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:29,800
One for you.

51
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:32,840
One.

52
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,560
A'yan likes Jindou and Yuanbao so much.

53
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,840
Would he really part with them for you?

54
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:39,800
Of course.

55
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,600
I am his

56
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,760
only brother.

57
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,120
Brother!

58
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:49,760
Brother!

59
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:52,920
Brother!

60
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:56,040
Jindou and Yuanbao are missing.

61
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,560
Ah, missing?

62
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,760
Maybe they went out to play.

63
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,160
I don't know.

64
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,090
I'll go with you.

65
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,800
Jindou!

66
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,200
Yuanbao!

67
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,520
Brother, you stole my dog.

68
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,800
You stole my dog.

69
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,560
You stole a child's dog.

70
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,800
I didn't steal his dog.

71
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,880
It was you. You stole my dog.

72
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,160
I don't care.

73
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,090
Go back, go back.

74
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,840
I won't leave.

75
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,480
You stole my dog.

76
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,960
You stole both of the ones you gave me.

77
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:39,000
All lands belong to the king.

78
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,280
I didn't steal it.

79
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,120
I just took it in the dark.

80
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:45,760
Look, Pixiu.

81
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,200
Alright.

82
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:49,680
Don't be sad.

83
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,480
Don't blame your brother either.

84
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,880
He wanted to give me this puppy to play with,

85
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:59,370
so he accidentally took the wrong one.

86
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,880
Then keep this one, Sister Xiaoyue.

87
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:07,400
It's fine if it's for you.

88
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,760
Thank you,

89
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,400
Ayan.

90
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,240
Pixiu, let's run.

91
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,480
Do you like it?

92
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,280
You child-stealing dog.

93
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,240
I didn't steal.

94
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,480
Yes, you did.

95
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,799
I really didn't.

96
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:46,680
The experiencer's character goal is 85% complete.

97
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,720
There is news from General Song.

98
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,440
General Song sent a message saying

99
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:53,280
that he will arrive in the capital in 2 days.

100
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,400
When General Song arrives,

101
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:58,200
I will catch him off guard.
